Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 400
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Output gifs/blossom-repair.gif

Hide
Type "export PS1='darren@ForgeSworn.dev:bray $ '"
Enter
Type "alias claude=/Users/darren/WebstormProjects/bray/site/demos/bray-demo.sh"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show

Type "claude -p 'Use the blossom-repair tool to search for blob sha256 e3b0c44298fc1c149afbf4c8996fb92427ae41e4649b934ca495991b7852b855 on servers https://blossom.azzamo.net and https://nostr.media'"
Enter
Sleep 25s
